welcome_message_body: Welcome to Westminster, where historic landmarks, stunning architecture, and a rich cultural heritage await you. Explore the iconic Big Ben, Buckingham Palace, and the vibrant streets of this charming city. Enjoy your stay and make the most of your time in Westminster!
